rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0002
rows.name:
Want to try training again
with Kasumi's power?

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0004
rows.name:
That's one way, but isn't this
more of a strategy issue?

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0006
rows.name:
Now that Hugo and Wadatsumi
are back, we need to combine
everyone's strength.

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0007
rows.name:
That's right, you can count
on us. Right, Wadatsumi?

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0008
rows.name: Yes. We won't be outdone next time.

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0010
rows.name:
After we've revised our
strategy, let's head back
to the Orlato Mountain Pass.
